0just%20slashing%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22295f0843-0b20-49d2-b028-cd7342080cf9%5C%22%3EYounger%20customers'%20financial%20woes%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EChipotle's%20CEO%2C%20Scott%20Boatwright%2C%20said%20on%20an%20October%2029%20earnings%20call%20that%20the%2025%20to%2035%20age%20group%20is%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efacing%20financial%20issues%20%26quot%3Bincluding%20unemployment%2C%20increased%20student%20loan%20repayment%2C%20and%20slower%20real%20wage%20growth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20they%20were%20patronizing%20Chipotle%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20losing%20them%20to%20the%20competition.%20We're%20losing%20them%20to%20grocery%20and%20food%20at%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20Boatwright%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flunch-break-expensive-increasing-costs-employees-skipping-meals-ezcater-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efeel%20the%20pinch%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20feel%20the%20pullback%20from%20them%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECava's%20CEO%2C%20Brett%20Schulman%2C%20echoed%20Chipotle's%20concerns%20on%20a%20Tuesday%20earnings%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20recognize%20that%20today's%20environment%20is%20creating%20real%20pressures%20for%20consumers%2C%20especially%20younger%20guests%20who%20are%20making%20more%20deliberate%20choices%20about%20where%20they%20spend.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESweetgreen's%20finance%20chief%2C%20Jamie%20McConnell%2C%20said%20on%20a%20Thursday%20earnings%20call%20that%20spending%20from%20the%2025%20to%2035%20age%20group%2C%20which%20makes%20up%20about%2030%25%20of%20the%20chain's%20consumer%20base%2C%20was%20down%2015%25%20in%20the%20recent%20quarter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20was%20%26quot%3Bmost%20under%20pressure%2C%26quot%3B%20McConnell%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228365dac9-9602-4691-8ce4-f6e88cfe59e8%5C%22%3EFast%20food%20is%20winning%20over%20slop%20bowls%3C%2Fh2%3