technology%20like%20AI.%20It's%20new.%20It's%20different.%20It's%20complicated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20that%20if%20I%20wanted%20Rev%20to%20be%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20AI%2C%20I%20needed%20to%20go%20deeper%20into%20the%20subject.%20If%20we%20want%20to%20build%20a%20trustworthy%20AI%20product%20for%20our%20customers%2C%20we%20need%20to%20understand%20how%20it%20works.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20why%20I%20will%20be%20pursuing%20a%20part-time%20master's%20degree%20in%20AI%20at%20East%20Texas%20A%26amp%3BM%20University%20in%20spring%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228c68972d-d68d-4603-bb1f-7fad6afc6fab%5C%22%3EOnline%20courses%20can%20only%20get%20you%20so%20far%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETech%20companies%20don't%20expect%20their%20directors%20and%20VPs%20to%20write%20code.%20I%20still%20write%20code%20every%20day%2C%20but%20I%20recognize%20that%20it's%20not%20the%20value%20I%20provide%20to%20Rev.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20as%20managers%2C%20we%20need%20to%20be%20able%20to%20listen%20to%20a%20technical%20discussion%20and%20guide%20our%20engineers%20to%20see%20problems%20from%20a%20different%20perspective.%20The%20only%20way%20I%20can%20do%20that%20is%20by%20keeping%20myself%20up%20to%20date%20on%20the%20latest%20technologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20don't%20understand%20our%20code%20base%20and%20what%20we%20are%20trying%20to%20build%20at%20a%20fairly%20deep%20level%2C%20I%20cannot%20help%20my%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20I%20could%20have%20learned%20more%20about%20AI%20through%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Flearning%2Fleadership-management-coursera-edx-linkedin-learning-online-courses%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eonline%20courses%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20books%2C%20but%20most%20of%20what's%20available%20is%20superficial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20taken%20some%20excellent%20courses%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Flearning%2Fwhat-is-udemy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%