when%20it%20was%20rectified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20customer%20data%20leak%20was%20first%20reported%20on%20Wednesday%20by%20Forbes%2C%20which%20spoke%20with%20a%20customer%20who%20began%20filling%20in%20a%20Klarna%20credit%20application%20form%20and%20found%20it%20already%20contained%20details%20that%20appeared%20to%20belong%20to%20another%20customer.%20Forbes%20said%20it%20verified%20the%20authenticity%20of%20the%20form%20and%20that%20it%20contained%20another%20person's%20full%20name%2C%20birth%20date%2C%20and%20address.%20A%20Klarna%20spokesperson%20told%20the%20outlet%20the%20issue%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Brare%20scenario%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20the%20result%20of%20a%20system-wide%20issue%20or%20a%20customer%20data%20breach.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInternal%20Slack%20messages%20told%20a%20different%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsoftware-companies-squeezed-by-ai-alixpartners-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKlarna%20product%3C%2Fa%3E%20director%20wrote%20a%20Slack%20post%20containing%20an%20estimation%20of%20the%20financial%20impact%20of%20%26quot%3Bnot%20having%20proper%20Phone%20Recycle%20Protection.%26quot%3B%20In%20the%20post%2C%20the%20director%20wrote%20that%20288%2C000%20customer%20logins%20could%20be%20exposed%20to%20unauthorized%20access.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20email%20to%20Business%20Insider%2C%20Klarna%20said%20that%20the%20number%20was%20only%20%26quot%3Ba%20starting%20point%26quot%3B%20for%20its%20investigation%20and%20%26quot%3Bnot%20a%20number%20of%20impacted%20individuals.%26quot%3B%20It%20did%20not%20provide%20an%20exact%20number%20of%20customers%20affected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKlarna%20projected%20an%20average%20legal%20and%20remediation%20cost%20of%20%241%2C000%20per%20severe%20case%2C%20with%20the%20potential%20financial%20impact%20of%20%2441.8%20million%2C%20a%20Slack%20post%20written%20by%20Klarna's%20product%20director%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20Slack%20post%20also%20said%20of%20the%20affected%20accounts%2C%20%26quot%3BOut%20of%20them%20we%20estimate%20that%20roughly%2010%25%20of%20them%20are%20severe%20cases%20where%20new%20phone%20owners%20gain%20access%20to%20sensitive%20information%20such%20as%20Klarna%20Balance.%26quot%3B%20Klarna%20Balance%20is%20a%20digital%20wallet%20that%20allows%20customers%20to%20store%20funds%20from%20their%20bank%20accounts%20and%20earn%20cash%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20Slack%20post%20this%20week%20summarizing%20the%20incident%2C%20Klarna%20detailed%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20incident%20involves%20a%20recycled%20phone%20number%20issue%20where%20a%20consumer%20who%20recently%20acquired%20a%20new%20phone%20number%20was%20automatically%20logged%20into%20a%20Klarna%20account%20belonging%20to%20the%20previous%20owner%20of%20that%20phone%20number.%20This%20allowed%20the%20consumer%20to%20view%20personal%20details%20of%20the%20previous%20account%20owner%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20post%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20Klarna%20greenlit%20employees%20to%20execute%20a%20full%20patch.%20A%20product%20director%20said%20in%20a%20Slack%20post%20that%20Klarna's%20chief%20product%20officer%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fklarna-ceo-explains-why-its-important-to-promote-internally-jobs-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDavid%20Fock%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20authorized%20a%20full%20rollout%20of%20the%20login%20policy%20change%20to%20add%20email%20OTP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20messages%20also%20say%20Klarna%20was%20putting%20together%20a%20summary%20of%20what%20merchants%20can%20do%20about%20the%20issue%2C%20and%20they%20planned%20to%20share%20it%20with%20Fock%20and%20Klarna's%20chief%20operating%20officer%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fklarna-meet-the-leaders-behind-europes-most-valuable-private-company-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECamilla%20Giesecke%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20our%20senior%20leadership%20team%20became%20aware%20of%20potential%20vulnerabilities%20related%20to%20phone%20number%20recycling%2C%20we%20took%20immediate%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Klarna%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e6941961-1ca7-439d-bb74-c144087c7f7a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EKlarna%20grapples%20with%20the%20fallout%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20internal%20messages%2C%20as%20seen%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20show%20that%20Klarna%20has%20been%20contending%20with%20how%20to%20roll%20out%20a%20fix%20for%20the%20recycled%20phone%20data%20leak%20issue%20and%20was%20concerned%20it%20would%20impact%20its%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKlarna's%20product%20team%20discussed%20adding%20email%20OTP%20login%2C%20rather%20than%20only%20a%20text%20message%20OTP%20login%20via%20phone%2C%20internal%20Slack%20messages%20from%20August%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStaffers%20said%20at%20the%20time%20in%20Slack%20messages%20that%20adding%20the%20additional%20verification%20measure%20would%20have%20a%20negative%20impact%20on%20the%20conversion%20ratio%20for%20merchants%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20the%20number%20of%20visitors%20to%20a%20retail%20outlet%20who%20complete%20a%20sales%20transaction%20%E2%80%94%20because%20email%20OTP%20would%20be%20more%20time-consuming%20for%20customers%20than%20text%20message%20OTP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20November%20Slack%20message%20about%20the%20potential%20impact%20on%20the%20conversion%20rate%2C%20a%20data%20analytics%20manager%20said%20Klarna%20could%20see%20a%20drop%20amounting%20to%20a%20reduction%20in%20gross%20merchandise%20value%20of%20%2428.5%20million%20a%20month.%20The%20manager%20said%20that%20the%20amount%20%26quot%3Bwill%20not%20go%20unnoticed%20and%20will%20raise%20questions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20manager%20also%20wrote%20that%20%26quot%3Bwe%20don't%20know%20the%20real%20number%20of%20recycled%20phone%20number%20cases%26quot%3B%20and%20questioned%20whether%20the%20company%20was%20confident%20the%20issue%20was%20serious%20enough%20to%20justify%20risking%20a%20potential%20drop%20in%20conversion%20rates%20in%20one%20of%20its%20key%20markets%2C%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20he%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20suggesting%20not%20to%20improve%20things%26quot%3B%20and%20would%20rather%20invest%20time%20and%20resources%20in%20improved%20login%20flows%2C%20rather%20than%20rolling%20out%20a%20change%20with%20such%20a%20high%20financial%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20manager%20said%20Klarna%20%26quot%3Bconcluded%20that%20we%20can't%20roll%20out%20the%20changes%20needed%26quot%3B%20because%20%26quot%3Bthe%20impact%20on%20these%20strategic%20partner%5Bs%5D%20would%20just%20be%20too%20high.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKlarna%20said%20that%20it%20is%20continuing%20to%20investigate%20the%20issue%20thoroughly%20and%20%26quot%3Bwill%20report%20to%20the%20relevant%20regulatory%20authorities%20if%20required%2C%20which%20also%20includes%20notifying%20any%20potentially%20impacted%20consumers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22869f2b46-b765-4edb-9974-46ab348a23ae%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EKlarna%20had%20similar%20data%20incidents%20in%20the%20past%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20the%20first%20time%20the%20issue%20has%20occurred.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESupport%20tickets%20from%20three%20years%20ago%2C%20which%20were%20seen%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20show%20similar%20incidents%20dating%20back%20to%20at%20least%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Klarna%20disclosed%20a%20data%20breach%20incident%20caused%20by%20a%20%26quot%3Bfaulty%26quot%3B%20change%20to%20its%20app%2C%20which%20exposed%20customers'%20information%20to%20other%20customers%20for%20a%20period%20of%2031%20minutes.%20In%20a%20separate%20incident%2C%20the%20company%20was%20fined%20about%20%24733%2C000%20in%202024%20by%20a%20Swedish%20court%20for%20not%20giving%20users%20enough%20information%20about%20how%20it%20would%20st