0(Austria)%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F690b7112599d46a4ccc183f8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223101%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFeldkirch%20has%20a%20population%20of%20around%2036%2C000%20people.%3Cp%3ECarol%20Sachs%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Ch4%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22839d3de7-d0ec-483f-a4dc-cbf8503e59e3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E6%20things%20to%20do%20in%20Feldkirch%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh4%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMarvel%20at%20a%20medieval%20castle.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Built%20in%20the%2013th%20century%20by%20the%20Counts%20of%20Montfort%2C%20Feldkirch's%20Schattenburg%20Castle%20is%20now%20a%20landmark%20and%20museum%20showcasing%20medieval%20weaponry%2C%20Gothic%20art%2C%20and%20period%20clothing.%20An%20on-site%20restaurant%2C%20Gasthof%20Schattenburg%2C%20serves%20hearty%20Austrian%20dishes.%20%26quot%3BFrom%20the%20castle%2C%20you%20get%20sweeping%20views%20of%20red-tiled%20rooftops%20and%20the%20Alps%20in%20the%20background%2C%26quot%3B%20Gabellone%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EStop%20to%20see%20an%20ancient%20watchtower.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Also%20known%20as%20the%20'Cat%20Tower%2C'%20the%20Katzenturm%20is%20a%20prominent%20part%20of%20Feldkirch's%20skyline.%20Originally%20built%20in%201507%20as%20part%20of%20the%20town's%20fortifications%2C%20the%20tower%20stands%2040%20meters%20high%20with%20Vorarlberg's%20biggest%20bell%20inside%2C%20which%20weighs%207%2C500%20kilos%20and%20still%20chimes%20today.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EPeruse%20a%20street%20market.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EFeldkirch%20hosts%20twice-weekly%20farmers%20markets%20year-round.%20%26quot%3BMany%20visitors%20overlook%20the%20weekly%20markets%20where%20you%20can%20sample%20cheeses%2C%20cured%20meats%2C%20and%20breads%20from%20the%20surrounding%20farms%2C%26quot%3B%20Gabellone%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ELearn%20about%20the%20culture.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20town's%20cultural%20center%2C%20Montforthaus%20Feldkirch%2C%20opened%20in%202015%20and%20hosts%20many%20noteworthy%20exhibitions%2C%20concerts%2C%20and%20programs%2C%20from%20poetry%20slams%20to%20wine%20fairs.%20Some%20events%20take%20place%20in%20a%20former%20swimming%20pool-turned-performance%20space%20and%20venue.%20There's%20also%20the%20annual%20Poolbar%20music%20festival%2C%20which%20occurs%20over%20several%20weeks%20each%20summer%20and%20features%20programming%20centered%20on%20music%2C%20art%2C%20and%20creativity.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EEnjoy%20a%20leisurely%20walk.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAdmire%20Austria's%20natural%20beauty%20with%20a%20walk%20on%20a%20pedestrian%20trail%20in%20the%20scenic%20Walgau%20Valley%2C%20or%20along%20the%20Ill%20River%2C%20which%20runs%20through%20town.%20%26quot%3BIn%20summer%2C%20walking%20along%20its%20banks%20is%20a%20lovely%20way%20to%20see%20the%20town%20from%20a%20different%20angle%2C%26quot%3B%20Gabellone%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ETake%20a%20day%20trip.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThere's%20also%20much%20to%20discover%20in%20neighboring%20areas%20such%20as%20Lake%20Constance%2C%20with%20its%20boat%20rides%20and%20lakeside%20promenades%2C%20or%20Bregenz%2C%20known%20for%20its%20summer%20opera%20festival%20on%20the%20lake.%20Additionally%2C%20nearby%20ski%20resorts%20like%20Lech%20can%20be%20reached%20by%20bus%20or%20car.%20%26quot%3BThese%20side%20trips%20complement%20Feldkirch%20well%20without%20feeling%20rushed%2C%26quot%3B%20Gabellone%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224134%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Schattenburg%20Castle%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F690cbf3e7f37aa653f55831f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223100%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESchattenburg%20Castle%3Cp%3ECarol%20Sachs%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20exploring%2C%20travelers%20will%20find%20that%20Feldkirch%20is%20well-suited%20to%20satiate%20hungry%20appetites.%3C%2